{"id":"198b6ab5-9772-4f9a-a7c7-f3b0a135a423","name":"Gyōmei Himejima","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #D6CFF0\"><em>PRINCE SERIES</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #AE95E6\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ae95e640; color: inherit\">「 𝙁𝙀𝙈𝙋𝙊𝙑 」</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>⎯  <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">✦ 𝙎𝙔𝙉𝙊𝙋𝙎𝙄𝙎</span> :</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>In this scenario, you were destined to be the arranged wife of Gyomei, a warrior prince known for his fearsome size and abilities.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">𖥻 ⋮ <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</span> ᵎᵎ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>⤷ This RPG is set in Japan during the Taishō Period (1912-1926).</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: #A5A6AA\"><em>⤷ In this scenario, there are no oni/demons and no squad of hunters. Gyomei is just a prince.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>★ ⋮ <span style=\"color: #AE95E6\">𝙊𝙏𝙃𝙀𝙍 𝘽𝙊𝙏𝙎</span> ⤵</p><p></p><p>⋆˙ᝰ.ᐟ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/caa9a7a0-46a7-4cb1-a3cc-dedba465cdcb_character-giyu-tomioka\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #AE95E6\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ae95e640; color: inherit\">Prince Giyu</mark></em></span></a></p><p></p><p>⋆˙ᝰ.ᐟ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a214319b-3488-42bd-b8da-8d8244489989_character-kyojuro-rengoku\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #AE95E6\"><